Tool: CheetahO

Category: Photography

Description: Photo optimization and resize

Available functions:
1. Name: compressImage
   Description: Compresses an image to reduce its size without sacrificing quality.
   Input: {"imageUrl": "Required. String. The URL of the image to be compressed.", "compressionLevel": "Optional. Integer. The desired compression level (1-100). Default is 80."}
   Output: {"compressedImageUrl": "String. The URL of the compressed image.", "originalSize": "Integer. The original size of the image in bytes.", "compressedSize": "Integer. The compressed size of the image in bytes.", "compressionRatio": "Float. The compression ratio achieved."}

2. Name: resizeImage
   Description: Resizes an image to the specified dimensions without distorting the aspect ratio.
   Input: {"imageUrl": "Required. String. The URL of the image to be resized.", "width": "Optional. Integer. The desired width of the resized image.", "height": "Optional. Integer. The desired height of the resized image."}
   Output: {"resizedImageUrl": "String. The URL of the resized image.", "originalDimensions": "String. The original dimensions of the image in the format 'width x height'.", "resizedDimensions": "String. The resized dimensions of the image in the format 'width x height'."}

3. Name: convertImageFormat
   Description: Converts an image to a different format, such as JPG, PNG, or WebP.
   Input: {"imageUrl": "Required. String. The URL of the image to be converted.", "targetFormat": "Required. String. The desired format of the converted image (e.g., 'jpg', 'png', 'webp')."}
   Output: {"convertedImageUrl": "String. The URL of the converted image.", "originalFormat": "String. The original format of the image.", "convertedFormat": "String. The format of the converted image."}

4. Name: listSupportedFormats
   Description: Retrieves a list of supported image formats for conversion.
   Input: None
   Output: {"supportedFormats": "Array. A list of supported image formats for conversion (e.g., ['jpg', 'png', 'webp'])."}

