4. Name: addImage
   Description: Add an image to the platform with associated tags.
   Input: {"imageUrl": "Required. String. The URL of the image to be added.", "tags": "Optional. String. A comma-separated list of tags to associate with the image.", "sourceUrl": "Optional. String. The source URL of the image."}
